      "SourceString": "<text color=\"FFFFFFFF\" fontface=\"black\" size=\"20\" Case=\"AllCaps\">Genius comes in many forms - whether you're dangerously funny, creating havoc with wild plants, or flooding the island with your best intentions; it often comes along with a companion: madness. Become everyone’s nemesis with The Last Laugh bundle!</>\r\nIncludes:",
